{"tid":2300893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安心出行配上呢樣野就真係令人安心啦","createTime":"2020-11-26T01:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T04:21:08.000Z","uid":313425,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d1621ec9c3cf03d52b02898a69ed0c55b3435c18","tid":2300893,"uid":313425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:42:21.000Z","msg":"近排搞活動整QR code，頂你個肺班中學生真係好百厭，我釘個QR code出來有條友竟然同我用<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">Marker</span></span>畫左一劃上去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAq5f6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAq5f6X.png&h=bda92e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果全部中學生都掃唔到QR code做唔到活動。仆你個街如果日後餐廳同商場強制使用健康碼，而又<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">無CCTV影住</span></span>，容乜易俾人唔覺意畫兩畫上咁我仲點安心出行。<br />\n<br />\n實測環節<br />\n以下為正常QR code<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhVMK0F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhVMK0F.png&h=e0ecf818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下為惡作劇結果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trQXRF7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrQXRF7.png&h=fb8a15c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C3uHNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C3uHNN.png&h=ad97fa8c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLq5f7N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLq5f7N.png&h=2ecbfc24&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好彩我發現到<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">只要畫得唔大筆/唔深色，個QR code好似可以正常運作</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2M14wGy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2M14wGy.png&h=927cf56b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GynjkzT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGynjkzT.png&h=dfc8adc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n請賜教：有無高手可以教我最低限度要畫幾多/某d關鍵位置先可以破壞個QR code？<br />\n利申純學術討論，本人愛國愛黨並不支持所有破壞行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d919d1cc7040709d3a32c6a86b5cc9e06a5b30","tid":2300893,"uid":313425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed64bc28d23fb3a4883aa71126503a5b32f3d889","tid":2300893,"uid":313425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aa5f02de5869705d49ca72357913ad80642104","tid":2300893,"uid":313425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73021611d218a70d7f7a34810e05209409f92252","tid":2300893,"uid":313425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2ad28889e8edfd2239a72eaf43df7a59a7d894","tid":2300893,"uid":102343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"好似係四個角落果大點for 鏡頭係唔同角度都到detect 到qr code<br />\n<br />\n中間應該係代表個qr code裝住啲咩value /link<br />\n<br />\n所以4個角落加中間好影響一個qr code <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba3ae15d435f40362c57068b2be53b39c64851d","tid":2300893,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"我記得好似係對準個粒頭嗰個正方形<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"9f5207acd63e41237a04f1593c86c93f55352868","tid"